{"tid":1650121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有乜理由因為個別人仕一個蛋糕搞到全世界割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-12T21:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T23:40:38.000Z","uid":66557,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e940129d66f0ecfe87badaeaa6a75d2c783f9fdb","tid":1650121,"uid":66557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:50:16.000Z","msg":"我一路都係咁諗，個個噤嬲就好似比藍絲搵到我哋嘅弱點，下次佢哋又用同一方式滲透咁點算， 呢班友只係個別人士，唔通有幾個人行為非常仆街，我哋就要瓦解成個運動，放棄一路以嚟爭取緊嘅野？咁死咗嗰啲人點算？<br />\n<br />\n過兩日啲藍絲又走過嚟扮黃拎支香檳出嚟慶祝生日，咁你成班玻璃心咪又碎曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界乜嘢仆街都有，佢哋喺靈堂切撚完蛋糕，全世界99.99%一齊出嚟屌咪顯得我哋齊心，有乜理由要割蓆，直情唔合理！<br />\n<br />\n下次同一類事件，大大聲屌冇問題，但係屌完唔該focus喺主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93b3206157515f8698a0a0fb9a0136b799d10c7","tid":1650121,"uid":227441,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:52:06.000Z","msg":"其實係老豆搵仔佢地on9 道德高地又唔為大局為重on99"},{"pid":"80d2500242da30c0d6f1fa00a711da2e02b8dfae","tid":1650121,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:53:43.000Z","msg":"成場夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExkBvsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExkBvsm.jpg&h=de205520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cd8623f448fff0591fe207b5a2bdef7877dafc","tid":1650121,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:54:49.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t